title: [Icemule, Brewer's Alley]
description: Under the protection of the towering west wall, an odd assortment of ramshackle buildings appears in this back street.  Some artistic soul recently scraped the ice off the wall, revealing a multi-colored mural depicting a troupe of halflings performing for a crowd of onlookers.
